        <title>WORM AND INPUT SHAFT, WORM BEARING AND ADJUSTING CUP</title>
        <para>Inspect worm, tapered bearings, and adjusting cup for wear, cracks or brinneling. Inspect input shaft for
            bad sealing surface or twisted and otherwise damaged serrations. Replace the components that exhibit any of
            these conditions.
        </para>
